con:request.con:request:
<soapenv:Envelope xmlns:soapenv="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/envelope/" xmlns:ws="http://ws.api.meveo.org/">\r
   <soapenv:Header/>\r
   <soapenv:Body>\r
      <ws:createOrUpdate>\r
         <!--Optional:-->\r
         <createOrUpdateScriptInstanceRequest code="org.meveo.service.script.PostpaidOfferScript" description="SCRIPT_INSTANCE_POSTPAID">\r
            <!--Optional:-->\r
            <type>JAVA</type>\r
            <script>
            <![CDATA[
package org.meveo.service.script;

import java.math.BigDecimal;
import java.util.ArrayList;
import java.util.List;
import java.util.Map;

import org.meveo.admin.exception.BusinessException;
import org.meveo.api.dto.catalog.CounterTemplateDto;
import org.meveo.api.dto.catalog.OfferServiceTemplateDto;
import org.meveo.api.dto.catalog.OfferTemplateDto;
import org.meveo.api.dto.catalog.PricePlanDto;
import org.meveo.api.dto.catalog.RecurringChargeTemplateDto;
import org.meveo.api.dto.catalog.ServiceChargeTemplateRecurringDto;
import org.meveo.api.dto.catalog.ServiceChargeTemplateRecurringsDto;
import org.meveo.api.dto.catalog.ServiceChargeTemplateUsagesDto;
import org.meveo.api.dto.catalog.ServiceTemplateDto;
import org.meveo.api.dto.catalog.ServiceTemplatesDto;
import org.meveo.api.dto.catalog.ServiceUsageChargeTemplateDto;
import org.meveo.api.dto.catalog.UsageChargeTemplateDto;
import org.meveo.model.admin.User;
import org.meveo.model.crm.Provider;
import org.meveo.model.notification.InboundRequest;
import org.meveo.service.notification.InboundRequestService;
import org.json.simple.JSONArray;
import org.json.simple.JSONObject;
import org.json.simple.parser.JSONParser;
import org.slf4j.Logger;
import org.slf4j.LoggerFactory;
import org.meveo.api.billing.WalletApi;
import org.meveo.api.catalog.OfferTemplateApi;
import org.meveo.api.catalog.ServiceTemplateApi;
import org.meveo.api.catalog.RecurringChargeTemplateApi;
import org.meveo.api.catalog.UsageChargeTemplateApi;
import org.meveo.api.catalog.CounterTemplateApi;
import org.meveo.api.catalog.PricePlanApi;
import org.meveo.model.catalog.CounterTemplateLevel;

/**
 * 
 * @author Seb
 * Edited 06/04/2016 00:56
 * Edited 17/04/2016       : set Prorated at termination too
 *                         : set Param1 as serviceCode
 * 
 */

public class PostpaidOfferScript extends Script {
	  
  	private static final Logger log = LoggerFactory.getLogger(PostpaidOfferScript.class);
  	InboundRequestService inboundRequestService = (InboundRequestService) getServiceInterface("InboundRequestService"); 
  	OfferTemplateApi offerTemplateApi = (OfferTemplateApi) getServiceInterface("OfferTemplateApi");
  	ServiceTemplateApi serviceTemplateApi = (ServiceTemplateApi) getServiceInterface("ServiceTemplateApi");
  	RecurringChargeTemplateApi recurringChargeTemplateApi = (RecurringChargeTemplateApi) getServiceInterface("RecurringChargeTemplateApi");
  	UsageChargeTemplateApi usageChargeTemplateApi = (UsageChargeTemplateApi) getServiceInterface("UsageChargeTemplateApi");
  	CounterTemplateApi counterTemplateApi = (CounterTemplateApi) getServiceInterface("CounterTemplateApi");
  	PricePlanApi pricePlanApi = (PricePlanApi)  getServiceInterface("PricePlanApi");
  	

  	@Override
	public void execute(Map<String,Object> context, User user) throws BusinessException{
		log.debug("start postpaidOffer creation script... event = {}",context.get("event"));
		InboundRequest req = (InboundRequest)context.get("event");
		inboundRequestService.create(req,user);
		log.debug("req.body = {}",req.getBody());
		String result = "{\"result\":\"OK\"}";
		try{
			JSONParser jsonParser =  new JSONParser();	
			JSONObject jsonReq = (JSONObject) jsonParser.parse(req.getBody());
			String offerCode = (String) jsonReq.get("code");
			log.debug("offerCode={}",offerCode);
			String name = (String) jsonReq.get("name");
			String description = (String) jsonReq.get("description");
			Double recurringPrice = jsonReq.get("recurringPrice") == null ? null : Double.valueOf(jsonReq.get("recurringPrice").toString());			
			Boolean proratedSubscription = (Boolean) jsonReq.get("proratedSubscription");
			String invoiceSubcategory = (String) jsonReq.get("invoiceSubcategory");
			JSONArray services =  (JSONArray) jsonReq.get("services");
			log.debug("create offer");
			OfferTemplateDto offerDto = new OfferTemplateDto();
			offerDto.setCode(offerCode);
			offerDto.setDescription(name);

			List<OfferServiceTemplateDto> offerServiceTemplates = new ArrayList<OfferServiceTemplateDto>();
			//ServiceTemplatesDto serviceTemplatesDto = new ServiceTemplatesDto();
			
			//abonnement
			RecurringChargeTemplateDto rct = new RecurringChargeTemplateDto();
			rct.setAmountEditable(Boolean.FALSE);
			rct.setApplyInAdvance(Boolean.TRUE);
			rct.setCalendar("MONTHLY");
			rct.setDescription("Abonnement");
			rct.setCode(offerCode+"_ABO_REC");
			rct.setInvoiceSubCategory("ABO_"+invoiceSubcategory);
			rct.setSubscriptionProrata(proratedSubscription);
			rct.setTerminationProrata(proratedSubscription);
			recurringChargeTemplateApi.create(rct,user);
			
			PricePlanDto rpp = new PricePlanDto();
			rpp.setCode(offerCode+"_ABO_PP");
			rpp.setAmountWithoutTax(BigDecimal.valueOf(recurringPrice));
			rpp.setDescription("Abonnement a offre "+offerCode);
			rpp.setPriority(10);
			rpp.setEventCode(offerCode+"_ABO_REC");
			pricePlanApi.create(rpp,user);
			
			ServiceTemplateDto aboServiceTemplateDto= new ServiceTemplateDto(offerCode+"_ABO_SV");
			aboServiceTemplateDto.setDescription("Abonnement");
			ServiceChargeTemplateRecurringsDto aboRecs = new ServiceChargeTemplateRecurringsDto();
			ServiceChargeTemplateRecurringDto aboRec = new ServiceChargeTemplateRecurringDto();
			aboRec.setCode(offerCode+"_ABO_REC");
			aboRecs.getServiceChargeTemplateRecurring().add(aboRec);
			aboServiceTemplateDto.setServiceChargeTemplateRecurrings(aboRecs);
			serviceTemplateApi.create(aboServiceTemplateDto,user);
			OfferServiceTemplateDto aboOstDto=new OfferServiceTemplateDto();
			aboOstDto.setServiceTemplate(aboServiceTemplateDto);
			offerServiceTemplates.add(aboOstDto);

			if(services!=null){
				for(Object o:services){
					JSONObject service = (JSONObject)o;
					String code = (String)service.get("code");
					String descr = (String)service.get("description");
					Double counter = service.get("counter") == null ? null : Double.valueOf( service.get("counter").toString());
					Double priceInCounter = service.get("priceInCounter") == null ? null : Double.valueOf( service.get("priceInCounter").toString());
					Double priceOverCounter = service.get("priceOverCounter") == null ? null : Double.valueOf(  service.get("priceOverCounter").toString());					Boolean mandatory =(Boolean) service.get("mandatory");
					String invoiceSubcat = (String)service.get("invoiceSubcategory");
					ServiceTemplateDto serviceTemplateDto= new ServiceTemplateDto(offerCode+"_"+code);
					serviceTemplateDto.setDescription(descr);
					//usages
					ServiceChargeTemplateUsagesDto usgs = new ServiceChargeTemplateUsagesDto();
						
					if(counter>0){
						CounterTemplateDto counterTemplateDto=new CounterTemplateDto();
						//counter
						CounterTemplateDto cnt = new CounterTemplateDto();
						cnt.setCode(offerCode+"_"+code+"_CNT");
						cnt.setCounterLevel(CounterTemplateLevel.UA);
						cnt.setDescription("compteur "+code);
						cnt.setCeiling(BigDecimal.valueOf(counter));
						cnt.setCalendar("MONTHLY");
						counterTemplateApi.create(cnt,user);
						
						//usage charge in counter
						UsageChargeTemplateDto usg = new UsageChargeTemplateDto();
						usg.setAmountEditable(Boolean.FALSE);
						usg.setDescription(descr);
						usg.setCode(offerCode+"_"+code+"_IN");
						usg.setInvoiceSubCategory("SERV_"+invoiceSubcat);
						usg.setFilterParam1(serviceTemplateDto.getCode());
						usageChargeTemplateApi.create(usg,user);
						
						ServiceUsageChargeTemplateDto usageInDto = new ServiceUsageChargeTemplateDto();
						usageInDto.setCode(offerCode+"_"+code+"_IN");
						usageInDto.setCounterTemplate(offerCode+"_"+code+"_CNT");
						usgs.getServiceChargeTemplateUsage().add(usageInDto);
						

						PricePlanDto rppin = new PricePlanDto();
						rppin.setCode(offerCode+"_"+code+"_IN_PP");
						rppin.setAmountWithoutTax(BigDecimal.valueOf(priceInCounter));
						rppin.setDescription("Prix "+offerCode+" dans le compteur");
						rppin.setPriority(10);
						rppin.setEventCode(offerCode+"_"+code+"_IN");
						pricePlanApi.create(rppin,user);
					}
					//usage charge out counter
					UsageChargeTemplateDto usg = new UsageChargeTemplateDto();
					usg.setAmountEditable(Boolean.FALSE);
					usg.setDescription(descr);
					usg.setCode(offerCode+"_"+code+"_OVER");
					usg.setInvoiceSubCategory("SERV_"+invoiceSubcat);
					usg.setFilterParam1(serviceTemplateDto.getCode());
					usageChargeTemplateApi.create(usg,user);
					

					PricePlanDto rppout = new PricePlanDto();
					rppout.setCode(offerCode+"_"+code+"_OVER_PP");
					rppout.setAmountWithoutTax(BigDecimal.valueOf(priceOverCounter));
					rppout.setDescription("Prix "+offerCode+" hors compteur");
					rppout.setPriority(10);
					rppout.setEventCode(offerCode+"_"+code+"_OVER");
					pricePlanApi.create(rppout,user);
					
					ServiceUsageChargeTemplateDto usageInDto = new ServiceUsageChargeTemplateDto();
					usageInDto.setCode(offerCode+"_"+code+"_OVER");
					usgs.getServiceChargeTemplateUsage().add(usageInDto);					
					serviceTemplateDto.setServiceChargeTemplateUsages(usgs);
					serviceTemplateApi.create(serviceTemplateDto,user);
					OfferServiceTemplateDto ostDto=new OfferServiceTemplateDto();
					ostDto.setServiceTemplate(serviceTemplateDto);
					offerServiceTemplates.add(ostDto);
				}
			}

			offerDto.setOfferServiceTemplates(offerServiceTemplates);
			offerTemplateApi.create(offerDto,user);
		} catch(Exception e){
			result = "{\"result\":\"KO\",\"err\":\""+e.getMessage()+"\"}";
			e.printStackTrace();
		}
		req.setResponseBody(result);
		req.getResponseHeaders().put("Content-type", "application/json");
		log.debug("req.setResponseBody({}) in req={}",result,req);
	}
}
]]>
            </script>\r
         </createOrUpdateScriptInstanceRequest>\r
      </ws:createOrUpdate>\r
   </soapenv:Body>\r
</soapenv:Envelope>

/**

public class PrepaidOfferScript extends Script {
	  
  	private static final Logger log = LoggerFactory.getLogger(PrepaidOfferScript.class);
  	InboundRequestService inboundRequestService = (InboundRequestService) getServiceInterface("InboundRequestService"); 
  	OfferTemplateApi offerTemplateApi = (OfferTemplateApi) getServiceInterface("OfferTemplateApi");

  	CounterTemplateApi counterTemplateApi = (CounterTemplateApi) getServiceInterface("CounterTemplateApi");
  	PricePlanApi pricePlanApi = (PricePlanApi)  getServiceInterface("PricePlanApi");
  	WalletApi walletApi = (WalletApi)  getServiceInterface("WalletApi");

  	@Override
	public void execute(Map<String,Object> context, User user) throws BusinessException{
		log.debug("start prepaidOfferScript creation script... event = {}",context.get("event"));
		InboundRequest req = (InboundRequest)context.get("event");
		inboundRequestService.create(req,user);
		log.debug("req.body = {}",req.getBody());
		String result = "{\"result\":\"OK\"}";
		try{
			JSONParser jsonParser =  new JSONParser();	
			JSONObject jsonReq = (JSONObject) jsonParser.parse(req.getBody());
			String offerCode = (String) jsonReq.get("code");
			log.debug("offerCode={}",offerCode);
			String name = (String) jsonReq.get("name");
			String description = (String) jsonReq.get("description");
			Double recurringPrice = jsonReq.get("recurringPrice") == null ? null : Double.valueOf(jsonReq.get("recurringPrice").toString());		
			Boolean proratedSubscription = (Boolean) jsonReq.get("proratedSubscription");
			String invoiceSubcategory = (String) jsonReq.get("invoiceSubcategory");
			JSONArray services =  (JSONArray) jsonReq.get("services");
			log.debug("create offer");
			OfferTemplateDto offerDto = new OfferTemplateDto();
			offerDto.setCode(offerCode);
			offerDto.setDescription(name);
			List<OfferServiceTemplateDto> offerServiceTemplates = new ArrayList<OfferServiceTemplateDto>();
			
			WalletTemplateDto walletTemplateDto = new WalletTemplateDto();
			walletTemplateDto.setCode("PREPAID");
			walletTemplateDto.setDescription("Prepaid wallet");
			walletTemplateDto.setWalletType(BillingWalletTypeEnum.PREPAID);
			walletApi.createOrUpdate(walletTemplateDto, user);
			log.debug("Prepaid wallet created");
			
			WalletsDto walletsDto = new WalletsDto();
			walletsDto.setWallet(Arrays.asList(walletTemplateDto.getCode()));
			
			//abonnement
			RecurringChargeTemplateDto rct = new RecurringChargeTemplateDto();
			rct.setAmountEditable(Boolean.FALSE);
			rct.setApplyInAdvance(Boolean.TRUE);
			rct.setCalendar("MONTHLY");
			rct.setDescription("Abonnement");
			rct.setCode(offerCode+"_ABO_REC");
			rct.setInvoiceSubCategory("ABO_"+invoiceSubcategory);
			rct.setSubscriptionProrata(proratedSubscription);
			recurringChargeTemplateApi.create(rct,user);
			
			PricePlanDto rpp = new PricePlanDto();
			rpp.setCode(offerCode+"_ABO_PP");
			rpp.setAmountWithoutTax(BigDecimal.valueOf(recurringPrice));
			rpp.setDescription("Abonnement a offre "+offerCode);
			rpp.setPriority(10);
			rpp.setEventCode(offerCode+"_ABO_REC");
			pricePlanApi.create(rpp,user);
			
			ServiceTemplateDto aboServiceTemplateDto= new ServiceTemplateDto(offerCode+"_ABO_SV");
			aboServiceTemplateDto.setDescription("Abonnement");
			ServiceChargeTemplateRecurringsDto aboRecs = new ServiceChargeTemplateRecurringsDto();
			ServiceChargeTemplateRecurringDto aboRec = new ServiceChargeTemplateRecurringDto();
			aboRec.setCode(offerCode+"_ABO_REC");
			aboRecs.getServiceChargeTemplateRecurring().add(aboRec);
			aboServiceTemplateDto.setServiceChargeTemplateRecurrings(aboRecs);
			serviceTemplateApi.create(aboServiceTemplateDto,user);
			OfferServiceTemplateDto aboOstDto=new OfferServiceTemplateDto();
			aboOstDto.setServiceTemplate(aboServiceTemplateDto);
			offerServiceTemplates.add(aboOstDto);

			if(services!=null){
				for(Object o:services){
					JSONObject service = (JSONObject)o;
					String code = (String)service.get("code");
					String descr = (String)service.get("description");
					Double counter = service.get("counter") == null ?null : Double.valueOf( service.get("counter").toString());
	                Double priceInCounter = service.get("priceInCounter") == null ? null : Double.valueOf( service.get("priceInCounter").toString());
					Double priceOverCounter = service.get("priceOverCounter") == null ? null : Double.valueOf(  service.get("priceOverCounter").toString());					
					Boolean mandatory =(Boolean) service.get("mandatory");					
					String invoiceSubcat = (String)service.get("invoiceSubcategory");
					ServiceTemplateDto serviceTemplateDto= new ServiceTemplateDto(offerCode+"_"+code);
					serviceTemplateDto.setDescription(descr);
					//usages
					ServiceChargeTemplateUsagesDto usgs = new ServiceChargeTemplateUsagesDto();
						
					if(counter>0){
						CounterTemplateDto counterTemplateDto=new CounterTemplateDto();
						//counter
						CounterTemplateDto cnt = new CounterTemplateDto();
						cnt.setCode(offerCode+"_"+code+"_CNT");
						cnt.setCounterLevel(CounterTemplateLevel.UA);
						cnt.setDescription("compteur "+code);
						cnt.setCeiling(new BigDecimal(counter));
						cnt.setCalendar("MONTHLY");
						counterTemplateApi.create(cnt,user);
						
						//usage charge in counter
						UsageChargeTemplateDto usg = new UsageChargeTemplateDto();
						usg.setAmountEditable(Boolean.FALSE);
						usg.setDescription(descr);
						usg.setCode(offerCode+"_"+code+"_IN");
						usg.setInvoiceSubCategory("SERV_"+invoiceSubcat);
						usg.setFilterParam1(serviceTemplateDto.getCode());
						usageChargeTemplateApi.create(usg,user);
						
						ServiceUsageChargeTemplateDto usageInDto = new ServiceUsageChargeTemplateDto();
						usageInDto.setCode(offerCode+"_"+code+"_IN");
						usageInDto.setCounterTemplate(offerCode+"_"+code+"_CNT");
						usageInDto.setWallets(walletsDto);
						usgs.getServiceChargeTemplateUsage().add(usageInDto);
						

						PricePlanDto rppin = new PricePlanDto();
						rppin.setCode(offerCode+"_"+code+"_IN_PP");
						rppin.setAmountWithoutTax(BigDecimal.valueOf(priceInCounter));
						rppin.setDescription("Prix "+offerCode+" dans le compteur");
						rppin.setPriority(10);
						rppin.setEventCode(offerCode+"_"+code+"_IN");
						pricePlanApi.create(rppin,user);
					}
					//usage charge out counter
					UsageChargeTemplateDto usg = new UsageChargeTemplateDto();
					usg.setAmountEditable(Boolean.FALSE);
					usg.setDescription(descr);
					usg.setCode(offerCode+"_"+code+"_OVER");
					usg.setInvoiceSubCategory("SERV_"+invoiceSubcat);
					usg.setFilterParam1(serviceTemplateDto.getCode());
					usageChargeTemplateApi.create(usg,user);
					

					PricePlanDto rppout = new PricePlanDto();
					rppout.setCode(offerCode+"_"+code+"_OVER_PP");
					rppout.setAmountWithoutTax(BigDecimal.valueOf(priceOverCounter));
					rppout.setDescription("Prix "+offerCode+" hors compteur");
					rppout.setPriority(10);
					rppout.setEventCode(offerCode+"_"+code+"_OVER");
					pricePlanApi.create(rppout,user);
					
					ServiceUsageChargeTemplateDto usageInDto = new ServiceUsageChargeTemplateDto();
					usageInDto.setCode(offerCode+"_"+code+"_OVER");
					usgs.getServiceChargeTemplateUsage().add(usageInDto);
					usageInDto.setWallets(walletsDto);
					serviceTemplateDto.setServiceChargeTemplateUsages(usgs);
					serviceTemplateApi.create(serviceTemplateDto,user);
					OfferServiceTemplateDto ostDto=new OfferServiceTemplateDto();
					ostDto.setServiceTemplate(serviceTemplateDto);
					offerServiceTemplates.add(ostDto);
				}
			}

			offerDto.setOfferServiceTemplates(offerServiceTemplates);
			offerTemplateApi.create(offerDto,user);

		} catch(Exception e){
			result = "{\"result\":\"KO\",\"err\":\""+e.getMessage()+"\"}";
			e.printStackTrace();
		}
		req.setResponseBody(result);
		req.getResponseHeaders().put("Content-type", "application/json");
		log.debug("req.setResponseBody({}) in req={}",result,req);
	}
}
]]>
            </script>\r
         </createOrUpdateScriptInstanceRequest>\r
      </ws:createOrUpdate>\r
   </soapenv:Body>\r
</soapenv:Envelope>
